{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Drawing text","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Drawing_text","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API\"><strong>Canvas API</strong></a></li>\n  <li class=\"toggle\">\n    <details open=\"\">\n      <summary>Canvas tutorial</summary>\n      <ol>\n        <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Basic_usage\">Basic usage</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Drawing_shapes\">Drawing shapes</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Applying_styles_and_colors\">Applying styles and colors</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Drawing_text\">Drawing text</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Using_images\">Using images</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Transformations\">Transformations</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Compositing\">Compositing and clipping</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Basic_animations\">Basic animations</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Advanced_animations\">Advanced animations</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Pixel_manipulation_with_canvas\">Pixel manipulation</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Optimizing_canvas\">Optimizing the canvas</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Finale\">Finale</a></li>\n        </ol>\n    </details>\n  </li>\n  <li class=\"toggle\">\n    <details open=\"\">\n      <summary>Examples</summary>\n      <ol>\n        <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/A_basic_ray-caster\">A basic raycaster</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Manipulating_video_using_canvas\">Manipulating video using canvas</a></li>\n      </ol>\n    </details>\n  </li>\n  <li class=\"toggle\">\n    <details open=\"\">\n      <summary>Interfaces</summary>\n      <ol>\n        <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement</code></a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D</code></a></li>\n        <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasGradient\"><code>CanvasGradient</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n        <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasPattern\"><code>CanvasPattern</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n        <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageBitmap\"><code>ImageBitmap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n        <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageData\"><code>ImageData</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n        <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextMetrics\"><code>TextMetrics</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n        <li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg> <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Path2D\"><code>Path2D</code></a></li>\n      </ol>\n    </details>\n  </li>\n  <li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/MDN\">Documentation:</a></strong></li>\n  <li class=\"toggle\">\n    <details>\n      <summary>Contribute</summary>\n      <ol>\n        <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/MDN\">The MDN project</a></li>\n      </ol>\n    </details>\n  </li>\n </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"> <ul class=\"prev-next\">\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Applying_styles_and_colors\">« Previous</a></li>\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Using_images\">Next  »</a></li>\n</ul></div>\n\n<div class=\"summary\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p>Após entender como <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Applying_styles_and_colors\">aplicar estilos e cores</a>&nbsp;no capítulo anterior, nós veremos agora como desenhar&nbsp;texto dentro do contexto de&nbsp;uma canvas.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"desenhando_texto","title":"Desenhando texto","isH3":false,"content":"<p>O context de renderização da canvas fornece dois métodos para renderização textual:&nbsp;</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"filltexttext_x_y_maxwidth_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/fillText\"><code>fillText(text, x, y [, maxWidth])</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Preenche com&nbsp;um determinado texto as cordenadas (x,y) recebidas.&nbsp;Opcionalmente com uma largura máxima para o desenho.</dd>\n <dt id=\"stroketexttext_x_y_maxwidth_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/strokeText\"><code>strokeText(text, x, y [, maxWidth])</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Traçeja um determinado texto nas cordenadas&nbsp;(x,y) recebidas. Opcionalmente com uma largura máxima para o desenho.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"um_exemplo_com_filltext","title":"Um exemplo com&nbsp;<code>fillText</code>","isH3":true,"content":"<p>O texto&nbsp;a seguir é rederizado utilizando <code>fillStyle</code>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js;highlight[4] notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">draw</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> ctx <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'canvas'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getContext</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'2d'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  ctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>font <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'48px serif'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  ctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">fillText</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Hello world'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">50</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n\n\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Um exemplo com&nbsp;fillText\" id=\"frame_a_filltext_example\" width=\"310\" height=\"110\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Drawing_text/_sample_.a_filltext_example.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>","titleAsText":"Um exemplo com fillText"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"um_exemplo_com_stroketext","title":"Um exemplo com&nbsp;<code>strokeText</code>","isH3":true,"content":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p dir=\"ltr\" id=\"tw-target-text\">O texto é preenchido usando o strokeStyle atual.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js;highlight[4] notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">draw</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> ctx <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'canvas'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getContext</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'2d'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  ctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>font <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'48px serif'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  ctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">strokeText</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Hello world'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">50</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n\n\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Um exemplo com&nbsp;strokeText\" id=\"frame_a_stroketext_example\" width=\"310\" height=\"110\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Drawing_text/_sample_.a_stroketext_example.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>","titleAsText":"Um exemplo com strokeText"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"estilo_de_texto","title":"<strong>Estilo de&nbsp;Texto</strong>","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Nos exemplos anteriores, já usamos&nbsp;a propriedade font para tornar o texto um pouco maior que o tamanho padrão. Existem mais algumas propriedades que permitem ajustar a maneira como o texto é exibido no canvas:</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"font_value_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/font\"><code>font = value</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>The current text style being used when drawing text. This string uses the same syntax as the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS\">CSS</a> <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/font\"><code>font</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> property. The default font is 10px sans-serif.</dd>\n <dt id=\"textalign_value_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/textAlign\"><code>textAlign = value</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Text alignment setting. Possible values: <code>start</code>, <code>end</code>, <code>left</code>, <code>right</code> or <code>center</code>. The default value is <code>start</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"textbaseline_value_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/textBaseline\"><code>textBaseline = value</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Baseline alignment setting. Possible values: <code>top</code>, <code>hanging</code>, <code>middle</code>, <code>alphabetic</code>, <code>ideographic</code>, <code>bottom</code>. The default value is <code>alphabetic</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"direction_value_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/direction\"><code>direction = value</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Directionality. Possible values: <code>ltr</code>, <code>rtl</code>, <code>inherit</code>. The default value is <code>inherit</code>.</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<p>Essas propriedades podem ser similares para você, se você trabalhou com CSS antes.</p>\n\n<p>O diagrama seguinte do&nbsp;<a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.whatwg.org/\" rel=\" noopener\">WHATWG</a> demonstra as várias baselines suportadas pela propriedade do&nbsp;<code>textBaseline</code><img alt=\"The top of the em square is\nroughly at the top of the glyphs in a font, the hanging baseline is\nwhere some glyphs like आ are anchored, the middle is half-way\nbetween the top of the em square and the bottom of the em square,\nthe alphabetic baseline is where characters like Á, ÿ,\nf, and Ω are anchored, the ideographic baseline is\nwhere glyphs like 私 and 達 are anchored, and the bottom\nof the em square is roughly at the bottom of the glyphs in a\nfont. The top and bottom of the bounding box can be far from these\nbaselines, due to glyphs extending far outside the em square.\" src=\"http://www.whatwg.org/specs/web-apps/current-work/images/baselines.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>","titleAsText":"Estilo de Texto"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"o_exemplo_de_uma_textbaseline","title":"O exemplo de uma textBaseline","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Edite o código abaixo e veja as atualizações em tempo real no canvas.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js;highlight[2] notranslate\"><code>ctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>font <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'48px serif'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>textBaseline <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'hanging'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">strokeText</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Hello world'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Playable code sample\" id=\"frame_playable_code\" width=\"700\" height=\"360\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Drawing_text/_sample_.playable_code.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"advanced_text_measurements","title":"Advanced text measurements","isH3":false,"content":"<p>In the case you need to obtain more details about the text, the following method allows you to measure it.</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"measuretext_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/measureText\"><code>measureText()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Returns a <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextMetrics\"><code>TextMetrics</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> object containing the width, in pixels, that the specified text will be when drawn in the current text style.</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<p>The following code snippet shows how you can measure a text and get its width.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js;highlight[3] notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">draw</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> ctx <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'canvas'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getContext</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'2d'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> text <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> ctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">measureText</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'foo'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// TextMetrics object</span>\n  text<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>width<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 16;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notas_específicas_-_gecko","title":"Notas específicas - Gecko","isH3":false,"content":"<p>No Gecko (a engine de renderização do Firefox, Firefox OS e outras&nbsp;aplicações Mozilla), algumas APIs prefixadas&nbsp;foram&nbsp;implementadas em&nbsp;versões anteriores para&nbsp;escrever texto&nbsp;em&nbsp;um&nbsp;canvas. Essas APIs agora estão depreciadas e removidas, e não são mais garantidas para uso.</p>\n\n<p></p><ul class=\"prev-next\">\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Applying_styles_and_colors\">« Previous</a></li>\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Using_images\">Next  »</a></li>\n</ul><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Desenhando texto","id":"desenhando_texto"},{"text":"<strong>Estilo de&nbsp;Texto</strong>","id":"estilo_de_texto"},{"text":"Advanced text measurements","id":"advanced_text_measurements"},{"text":"Notas específicas - Gecko","id":"notas_específicas_-_gecko"}],"summary":"\nApós entender como aplicar estilos e cores no capítulo anterior, nós veremos agora como desenhar texto dentro do contexto de uma canvas.\n","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Text zeichnen","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Drawing text","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Dibujar texto usando canvas","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Dessin de texte avec canvas","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"テキストの描画","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"텍스트 그리기","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Rysowanie tekstu przy użyciu canvas","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Рисование текста","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"绘制文本","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"使用canvas繪製文字","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/canvas_api/tutorial/drawing_text","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/canvas_api/tutorial/drawing_text/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API","title":"Canvas"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial","title":"Canvas tutorial"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Drawing_text","title":"Drawing text"}],"pageTitle":"Drawing text - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}